Program: Outlook
Title: 'Death Row Couple' Find Love
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01c62wz
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 24 Jul 2013
How Sunny Jacobs and Peter Pringle found each other and love, after both were sentenced to death for crimes they had not committed. Peter's book is called About Time: Surviving Ireland's Death Row. Also 83-year-old Pablo Novak, who refuses to leave the Argentinian ghost town of Epecuen and American soul legend Bobby Womack looks back over a career spanning five decades. Show less